WEBVTT

01:37.930 --> 01:40.710
[Fate Chooses You]

01:41.350 --> 01:43.640
[Episode 18]

02:02.000 --> 02:03.950
Welcome out of seclusion, Father.

02:04.480 --> 02:06.410
Welcome out of seclusion, Father.

02:13.680 --> 02:17.380
[Xia Xuanzi]

02:15.870 --> 02:16.750
Gui is dead?

02:17.360 --> 02:18.030
Father,

02:18.430 --> 02:19.630
Gui's last message

02:19.910 --> 02:21.110
was three months ago.

02:21.190 --> 02:22.840
He'd been dispatched by the Qinghong Sect

02:22.840 --> 02:24.970
to the capital to protect an official.

02:34.680 --> 02:35.660
[Shou Gong]

02:50.560 --> 02:53.090
The one who killed Gui
has come to North Xiang.

02:53.280 --> 02:54.480
I'm going to meet her.

03:00.430 --> 03:00.960
Go.

03:02.080 --> 03:02.750
Find her.

03:10.400 --> 03:11.530
Prepare my clothes.

03:12.360 --> 03:12.910
Yes!

03:39.310 --> 03:39.870
Here.

03:40.800 --> 03:41.860
Careful, it's hot.

03:44.670 --> 03:46.070
Is it warm enough inside?

03:46.960 --> 03:48.090
Senior, you eat too.

04:00.710 --> 04:02.240
What are you up to this time?

04:02.240 --> 04:04.670
The temperature difference
between day and night here is huge.

04:04.670 --> 04:06.870
At night, the cold wind cuts to the bone.

04:06.920 --> 04:09.650
Immortals, you have to sleep
in this sleeping bag

04:10.000 --> 04:10.840
to rest well.

04:12.240 --> 04:13.240
Immortals, look.

04:13.630 --> 04:14.560
Open it up,

04:14.840 --> 04:16.769
and it's an enclosed sleeping bag.

04:17.120 --> 04:18.120
Sleeping inside,

04:18.269 --> 04:20.800
it's windproof, cold-proof, and bug-proof.

04:22.390 --> 04:23.750
How much is it?

04:25.040 --> 04:25.900
It has no price.

04:26.600 --> 04:28.480
Ever since Craftsman Zhu made it,

04:28.830 --> 04:31.120
it's never been sold on the market.

04:31.800 --> 04:32.390
Why?

04:33.600 --> 04:35.260
The immortal sects forbid it.

04:37.159 --> 04:37.800
Not just

04:38.510 --> 04:40.159
this sleeping bag—

04:40.830 --> 04:42.680
any novel and practical items

04:42.830 --> 04:44.390
invented by our kind

04:44.870 --> 04:45.830
are forbidden from

04:45.830 --> 04:47.230
being sold on the market.

04:49.310 --> 04:49.830
So

04:50.070 --> 04:52.560
that's why you went to Lingji Mountain
to steal books

04:52.560 --> 04:53.430
to learn

04:53.430 --> 04:54.950
the immortal sects' techniques?

04:54.950 --> 04:56.210
That wasn't stealing.

04:56.240 --> 04:56.830
We weren't

04:56.830 --> 04:58.230
after the immortal arts.

04:58.360 --> 05:00.270
We just went to copy
the Qiandie Five-Fire Technique

05:00.270 --> 05:02.390
from the Qiandie Scripture,
which originally

05:02.390 --> 05:03.950
belonged to our Artisan Clan.

05:03.950 --> 05:05.070
Wasn't the Qiandie Scripture

05:05.070 --> 05:06.600
created by Mr. Lin Ye,

05:06.920 --> 05:09.040
the seventh-generation leader
of Lingji Mountain?

05:09.040 --> 05:11.190
When Lin Ye once came to
the mortal world to cultivate,

05:11.190 --> 05:13.510
he happened to encounter
a master artisan of our clan

05:13.510 --> 05:14.800
forging iron and casting swords.

05:14.800 --> 05:15.870
He was struck by inspiration

05:15.870 --> 05:17.200
and stayed for a few days

05:17.270 --> 05:18.560
to learn this forging method

05:18.560 --> 05:19.960
from our master artisan.

05:20.070 --> 05:21.630
After he returned to Lingji Mountain,

05:21.630 --> 05:23.160
it was through this forging method

05:23.160 --> 05:24.920
that he came to comprehend
the Qiandie Scripture.

05:24.920 --> 05:25.520
Moreover,

05:25.800 --> 05:27.560
without the master artisan's permission,

05:27.560 --> 05:28.750
he recorded this method in detail

05:28.750 --> 05:30.430
in the scripture.

05:31.720 --> 05:33.180
You wandering swindlers,

05:33.270 --> 05:34.270
there's no lie

05:34.270 --> 05:35.470
you wouldn't make up.

05:35.510 --> 05:36.970
Immortal, you don't know.

05:37.270 --> 05:39.730
That master artisan's name
was Zhu Qiandie—

05:39.920 --> 05:42.360
the very grand ancestor of Craftsman Zhu.

05:43.070 --> 05:44.430
We...

05:44.450 --> 05:46.190
We did steal your money,

05:46.800 --> 05:47.680
but we...

05:48.310 --> 05:49.680
had no other choice.

06:02.360 --> 06:03.490
This is the last one.

06:03.920 --> 06:04.520
You eat it.

06:05.160 --> 06:05.750
No need.

06:06.920 --> 06:07.870
It's very good.

06:08.190 --> 06:10.920
I guess neither of you
has ever tried this before.

06:11.510 --> 06:12.640
Indeed, we haven't.

06:13.160 --> 06:14.830
This is called maize,

06:15.120 --> 06:16.680
also known as Golden Tassel.

06:16.680 --> 06:18.830
It can grow on dry hillsides

06:19.160 --> 06:20.630
and needs only a little water to survive.

06:20.630 --> 06:22.680
Moreover, the yield is high,
and it's easy to store.

06:22.680 --> 06:25.130
You can steam it, boil it,

06:25.160 --> 06:25.820
or roast it.

06:26.150 --> 06:27.880
It can also be ground into flour

06:28.040 --> 06:29.500
and cooked into porridge.

06:29.600 --> 06:31.360
Yuedong has suffered severe droughts
in recent years.

06:31.360 --> 06:32.920
That region is mostly mountainous.

06:32.920 --> 06:34.980
If commoners could grow more of this,

06:35.430 --> 06:37.159
so many wouldn't have died.

06:38.120 --> 06:39.920
If it's really as good as you say,

06:39.920 --> 06:41.750
why don't you grow it yourselves?

06:41.750 --> 06:42.680
You'd have to

06:43.070 --> 06:44.930
ask your immortal sects about it.

06:45.270 --> 06:46.630
If you don't know how to speak properly,

06:46.630 --> 06:47.830
keep your mouth shut.

06:49.240 --> 06:50.500
She told you to shut up.

06:51.390 --> 06:54.070
Immortal sects need spiritual energy
for cultivation.

06:54.070 --> 06:54.680
Besides

06:54.950 --> 06:56.920
the naturally endowed blessed lands,

06:56.920 --> 06:57.580
spirit rice

06:57.750 --> 07:00.070
is one of the major sources
of spiritual energy.

07:00.070 --> 07:01.480
But spirit rice is rare.

07:01.920 --> 07:04.120
A full mu of land barely yields
a single bowl.

07:04.120 --> 07:06.050
Instructed by the immortal sects,

07:06.160 --> 07:08.190
the government encourages
the commoners to grow more rice

07:08.190 --> 07:10.600
while heavily taxing other crops.

07:10.800 --> 07:12.430
Especially the Golden Tassel—

07:12.430 --> 07:13.680
the government controls the seed supply

07:13.680 --> 07:15.390
and keeps squeezing people at every turn.

07:15.390 --> 07:17.510
There's no profit in it for the commoners,

07:17.510 --> 07:19.110
so they simply don't grow it.

07:21.000 --> 07:22.330
Then how did you get this?

07:22.330 --> 07:23.800
Seeds buried in the soil

07:23.920 --> 07:25.510
can sprout with just a little water.

07:25.510 --> 07:26.830
Just like dandelions—

07:27.000 --> 07:27.950
they take root

07:28.160 --> 07:29.600
wherever they land.

07:29.920 --> 07:31.510
The immortal sects may control
the Central Plains,

07:31.510 --> 07:32.950
but some grow in North Xiang.

07:32.950 --> 07:34.000
Even if they manage to

07:34.000 --> 07:35.310
control North Xiang in the future,

07:35.310 --> 07:36.040
who knows—

07:36.040 --> 07:37.530
somewhere in another remote ravine,

07:37.530 --> 07:39.530
the Golden Tassel might grow again.

07:39.750 --> 07:41.350
You can never wipe it all out.

07:41.480 --> 07:43.730
Just like this tower ship,

07:44.159 --> 07:46.090
everything leaves traces behind.

07:46.680 --> 07:48.010
They can't be wiped out.

07:48.120 --> 07:49.450
They can't be wiped out.

08:21.510 --> 08:22.630
Mother!

08:24.120 --> 08:25.870
Mother!

08:33.480 --> 08:34.030
Mother!

08:38.909 --> 08:39.510
Mother!

08:40.000 --> 08:41.600
Mother, where are you going?

08:41.909 --> 08:43.510
Mother, where are you going?

08:43.960 --> 08:45.270
Don't leave me behind.

08:45.870 --> 08:47.390
I will be good.

08:49.320 --> 08:51.270
Mother, don't leave me!

08:53.150 --> 08:55.720
Mother, don't leave me!

08:56.200 --> 08:57.000
Mother!

08:57.870 --> 09:00.000
You monster—neither human nor ghost—

09:00.480 --> 09:01.630
you should just die here!

09:01.630 --> 09:02.510
Mother!

09:12.030 --> 09:13.030
Mother!

09:17.670 --> 09:18.750
Mother!

09:20.790 --> 09:21.910
Mother!

09:24.750 --> 09:25.840
Mother!

10:36.360 --> 10:37.490
Have you seen Xunmu?

10:38.030 --> 10:40.120
Vajra Xunmu said the room was too stuffy

10:40.120 --> 10:41.480
and wanted to go out for some fresh air.

10:41.480 --> 10:42.120
Go find her

10:42.510 --> 10:43.910
and keep a close eye on her.

10:43.910 --> 10:44.510
Yes.

10:48.440 --> 10:49.910
Didn't you see me today?

10:50.720 --> 10:51.920
Why did you ignore me?

10:53.440 --> 10:54.370
What do you want?

10:56.790 --> 10:58.190
It's been so long since we

10:58.270 --> 11:00.200
last saw each other in the capital.

11:00.200 --> 11:01.630
I came to say hello.

11:03.270 --> 11:04.200
We're not close.

11:04.720 --> 11:05.480
Not close?

11:07.000 --> 11:08.080
But I know

11:08.080 --> 11:09.280
quite a lot about you.

11:10.480 --> 11:11.360
For instance,

11:11.840 --> 11:14.270
a certain female cultivator
killed Mr. Gui,

11:14.270 --> 11:16.510
provoking the Master of the Bishui Branch
to seek revenge.

11:16.510 --> 11:17.510
Right after that,

11:17.670 --> 11:19.550
a man showed up at their door

11:20.120 --> 11:21.920
and wiped out the entire branch.

11:23.270 --> 11:24.150
That was you,

11:24.720 --> 11:25.840
wasn't it?

11:27.630 --> 11:29.030
What exactly do you want?

11:29.670 --> 11:30.360
Scared?

11:32.150 --> 11:33.600
If I wanted to expose you,

11:33.870 --> 11:35.400
I would've done so already.

11:36.200 --> 11:37.130
Get to the point.

11:38.550 --> 11:40.240
Those three burdens you're traveling with

11:40.240 --> 11:42.120
don't look like cultivators.

11:42.960 --> 11:44.690
Now that you're in North Xiang,

11:44.960 --> 11:46.420
can you still act so tough?

11:51.440 --> 11:52.770
How about we make a deal?

11:53.720 --> 11:54.720
You help me kill Wenyin,

11:54.720 --> 11:55.790
that big brute,

11:56.440 --> 11:57.170
and I promise

11:58.240 --> 12:00.640
I won't cause you any trouble
in the future.

12:02.390 --> 12:03.240
That's all?

12:04.360 --> 12:05.600
What do you want then?

12:06.030 --> 12:06.960
I want you to

12:07.660 --> 12:08.990
help me find something.

12:10.790 --> 12:11.670
Let's hear it.

12:12.000 --> 12:13.000
Sunblock Banner.

12:15.240 --> 12:16.100
I don't believe

12:16.600 --> 12:17.840
there's anything in this world

12:17.840 --> 12:19.300
that money cannot settle.

12:19.390 --> 12:21.920
I'll give you 50 taels
for your superior room.

12:22.910 --> 12:23.600
No.

12:25.200 --> 12:26.200
Then 100 taels...

12:26.910 --> 12:28.040
for your entire inn.

12:29.270 --> 12:30.240
A hundred taels?

12:30.870 --> 12:32.930
That doesn't quite seem like enough.

12:33.240 --> 12:35.510
Then that means there's room to negotiate.

12:35.510 --> 12:36.570
Two hundred taels.

12:36.600 --> 12:37.120
Two...

12:40.840 --> 12:42.150
Money is a good thing—

12:42.150 --> 12:43.840
so long as you live long enough

12:45.000 --> 12:46.480
to spend it.

12:53.240 --> 12:54.510
You can stay in my room.

12:55.240 --> 12:56.040
Enchantress?

13:03.030 --> 13:03.670
Sir?

13:22.080 --> 13:22.600
Senior,

13:23.720 --> 13:25.000
what are you thinking about?

13:25.000 --> 13:25.910
I was thinking

13:26.600 --> 13:27.930
how we've never heard of

13:28.080 --> 13:29.940
any of the things they mentioned.

13:30.240 --> 13:31.570
The flying tower ships,

13:32.110 --> 13:34.150
indestructible mechanical puppets,

13:34.150 --> 13:34.790
and cannons with a range

13:34.790 --> 13:35.910
of over 100 zhang—

13:36.240 --> 13:37.960
we've never heard of any of them.

13:37.960 --> 13:39.090
Isn't that strange?

13:39.840 --> 13:41.120
If civilization

13:41.320 --> 13:42.450
among the Human Race

13:42.510 --> 13:43.510
had truly reached such heights

13:43.510 --> 13:44.440
over 1,000 years ago,

13:44.440 --> 13:45.370
as they claimed,

13:46.080 --> 13:46.910
then how could we have known

13:46.910 --> 13:48.390
absolutely nothing about it?

13:48.390 --> 13:50.080
If I hadn't seen it with my own eyes,

13:50.080 --> 13:51.360
I definitely would've thought

13:51.360 --> 13:52.560
they were lying to me.

13:53.390 --> 13:54.520
That's not strange.

13:55.240 --> 13:56.700
Everything can be buried.

13:57.080 --> 13:58.510
But as long as someone conceives of it,

13:58.510 --> 14:00.170
someone will bring it to life.

14:00.200 --> 14:01.630
Just like this desert—

14:02.200 --> 14:04.000
it's buried far too many things.

14:04.910 --> 14:05.480
Senior,

14:06.030 --> 14:08.110
none of this has anything to do with us.

14:08.110 --> 14:08.910
Doesn't it?

14:10.150 --> 14:10.720
No.

14:16.390 --> 14:16.960
Sheng,

14:17.480 --> 14:19.120
I remember you once told me

14:19.480 --> 14:21.360
that you're also from North Xiang.

14:21.360 --> 14:22.820
Where was your home again?

14:26.550 --> 14:27.600
I was wandering everywhere.

14:27.600 --> 14:28.860
How could I have a home?

14:30.750 --> 14:31.270
Senior,

14:31.550 --> 14:32.550
go to sleep early.

15:00.480 --> 15:01.080
Bite her.

15:02.240 --> 15:02.900
Go on, bite.

15:03.200 --> 15:03.870
Bite!

15:05.240 --> 15:06.170
Don't be afraid.

15:06.670 --> 15:08.510
Let my precious take a bite.

15:09.240 --> 15:10.510
It won't kill you!

15:14.840 --> 15:15.550
It bit you!

15:15.840 --> 15:16.650
I've fed this Baihua snake

15:16.650 --> 15:17.670
on poison sacs

15:17.670 --> 15:18.870
for a full 100 days.

15:19.200 --> 15:21.080
Just now I soaked it in pufferfish blood.

15:21.080 --> 15:22.000
This is the moment

15:22.000 --> 15:23.800
its poison is at its most potent!

15:24.390 --> 15:25.320
How do you feel?

15:26.670 --> 15:27.530
How do you feel?

15:33.200 --> 15:34.800
The poison has taken effect.

15:35.200 --> 15:36.530
Faster than I expected.

15:36.750 --> 15:37.630
Much faster.

15:38.000 --> 15:38.840
Great.

15:39.360 --> 15:40.270
Great!

15:43.000 --> 15:44.060
You have to hold on.

15:44.270 --> 15:45.200
You mustn't die,

15:45.510 --> 15:46.310
do you hear me?

15:46.630 --> 15:48.030
You absolutely cannot die!

15:48.030 --> 15:49.090
You must wait for me

15:49.670 --> 15:52.270
to refine
the Baihua Spirit-Nourishing Pill.

16:04.790 --> 16:06.360
Father has not yet seen...

16:07.080 --> 16:08.610
He'll never get to see it...

16:22.320 --> 16:23.270
Sheng,

16:23.840 --> 16:25.240
you'd better run faster.

16:26.510 --> 16:27.940
If I catch you,

16:29.320 --> 16:32.000
you'll wish you were dead.

17:06.589 --> 17:08.750
She's been poisoned
by Seventh Brother's snake.

17:08.750 --> 17:09.880
She can't get far.

17:10.589 --> 17:11.720
Split up and search!

17:29.890 --> 17:32.240
[Yunhan Inn]

17:31.200 --> 17:32.680
I remember your surname is Lu.

17:32.680 --> 17:33.480
How about this?

17:33.480 --> 17:34.140
From now on,

17:34.200 --> 17:35.130
I'll call you Lu.

17:36.070 --> 17:36.550
Lu,

17:37.030 --> 17:38.640
why did you come to North Xiang?

17:38.640 --> 17:41.240
Are you here on business
for Chongling Valley?

17:41.830 --> 17:42.690
What about you?

17:42.880 --> 17:44.210
What are you doing here?

17:45.110 --> 17:45.680
My father

17:46.160 --> 17:49.290
sent me here to deal with
a group of demonic cultivators.

17:50.640 --> 17:51.900
Demonic cultivators?

17:52.030 --> 17:52.830
That's right.

17:53.160 --> 17:53.920
It's a cult

17:54.270 --> 17:55.930
called the Wushuang Society.

17:56.720 --> 17:57.920
They recently

17:58.270 --> 17:59.750
stole from our family's Scripture Pavilion

17:59.750 --> 18:01.280
and injured our disciples.

18:01.590 --> 18:02.720
I heard that they've

18:02.940 --> 18:04.750
fled to North Xiang these past few days.

18:04.750 --> 18:05.310
Lu,

18:05.880 --> 18:07.210
let me tell you a secret.

18:07.270 --> 18:08.920
I've heard this group of
demonic cultivators

18:08.920 --> 18:10.450
is planning something big.

18:10.790 --> 18:12.070
If they succeed...

18:13.310 --> 18:15.440
things will become very troublesome.

18:19.350 --> 18:21.680
Are those people behind you your friends?

18:24.640 --> 18:25.160
Yes,

18:25.440 --> 18:26.100
my friends.

18:29.070 --> 18:30.160
I'm Lin Muhan,

18:30.350 --> 18:31.680
Young Sect Master
of Lingji Mountain.

18:31.680 --> 18:32.810
Nice to meet you all.

18:33.750 --> 18:35.310
-Nice to meet you.
-Nice to meet you.

18:35.310 --> 18:37.440
Lingji Mountain... an immortal sect!

18:40.350 --> 18:41.920
This buddy of mine aspires to
join an immortal sect

18:41.920 --> 18:43.160
and pursue cultivation,

18:43.160 --> 18:44.240
but he lacks the immortal perception.

18:44.240 --> 18:45.720
He's not destined to join you.

18:45.720 --> 18:46.720
Immortal sect...

18:47.440 --> 18:48.270
Why don't...

18:48.720 --> 18:49.960
we move him next door

18:50.350 --> 18:52.200
so as not to disturb your catch-up?

18:52.200 --> 18:52.680
Right!

18:53.350 --> 18:53.880
Let's go.

18:54.070 --> 18:54.600
Let's go.

19:01.960 --> 19:02.440
Come on.

19:07.160 --> 19:07.680
Lu,

19:08.440 --> 19:09.030
your friend

19:09.030 --> 19:10.400
looks seriously injured.

19:10.400 --> 19:11.790
Do you need any help?

19:13.590 --> 19:15.400
He was accidentally bitten
by something venomous.

19:15.400 --> 19:16.830
My friends have gone to find medicine.

19:16.830 --> 19:17.430
Medicine?

19:17.720 --> 19:18.510
You can just ask me.

19:18.510 --> 19:19.390
I brought some Yangyuan Pills.

19:19.390 --> 19:20.000
No need.

19:24.790 --> 19:25.240
But...

19:26.000 --> 19:27.000
how did you get involved

19:27.000 --> 19:28.330
with that enchantress?

19:29.510 --> 19:31.170
This enchantress is leaving.

19:32.960 --> 19:34.440
Don't forget our deal.

19:39.110 --> 19:39.790
What deal?

19:40.920 --> 19:41.510
Nothing.

19:44.640 --> 19:46.110
Since we've crossed paths,

19:46.110 --> 19:47.240
I ought to warn you—

19:48.000 --> 19:49.310
she is one of

19:49.310 --> 19:50.750
the Eight Vajras of the Qinghong Sect.

19:50.750 --> 19:52.010
She may look harmless,

19:52.030 --> 19:53.630
but she's actually perverse

19:53.790 --> 19:55.030
and ruthless.

19:55.400 --> 19:56.260
Think about it—

19:56.400 --> 19:57.680
having survived in a place

19:57.680 --> 19:58.270
like the Qinghong Sect

19:58.270 --> 19:59.350
and reached that position,

19:59.350 --> 20:00.480
could she be simple?

20:01.480 --> 20:01.960
No.

20:02.550 --> 20:04.010
You're too kind-hearted.

20:04.510 --> 20:06.240
You mustn't be deceived by her.

20:06.830 --> 20:07.720
I know.

20:21.550 --> 20:22.510
Sir, feel free to look around.

20:22.510 --> 20:23.440
Hey, attendant!

20:23.830 --> 20:24.830
A bowl of noodles.

20:27.510 --> 20:28.240
Take a look at this one.

20:28.240 --> 20:30.070
Meat buns. We have them all. Take a look.

20:30.070 --> 20:30.880
I'd like one.

20:31.830 --> 20:32.690
Stop. Don't go.

20:34.070 --> 20:35.600
Whose little buddy is this?

20:35.720 --> 20:36.830
Are you lost?

20:36.920 --> 20:38.320
Can't find your way home?

20:40.790 --> 20:41.920
Don't rush off.

20:42.160 --> 20:43.400
Where is your family?

20:43.590 --> 20:44.810
Do you want to come back with us?

20:44.810 --> 20:46.470
We'll help you find your home.

20:47.910 --> 20:48.600
Look at him—

20:49.140 --> 20:50.100
that face,

20:50.400 --> 20:51.480
those eyes...

20:52.270 --> 20:54.030
Perfect to sell to a wealthy household

20:54.030 --> 20:55.000
as a servant boy.

20:57.960 --> 20:59.070
Please stop, all of you.

20:59.070 --> 20:59.750
Let go.

21:00.160 --> 21:01.680
You're stirring up trouble.

21:01.680 --> 21:03.750
Be careful
you don't bring trouble upon yourselves.

21:03.750 --> 21:04.960
Today, I'll show you

21:04.960 --> 21:06.480
what real trouble looks like!

21:06.480 --> 21:06.960
Get him!

21:14.240 --> 21:15.170
This isn't over!

21:15.270 --> 21:16.270
Go. Let's go!

21:17.030 --> 21:18.290
You saved their lives,

21:19.240 --> 21:20.900
but they don't appreciate it.

21:21.830 --> 21:22.760
I walk my own path

21:23.400 --> 21:24.860
and do as my heart sees fit.

21:26.750 --> 21:29.210
Thank you, senior,
for sparing their lives.

21:31.480 --> 21:33.210
You're from Tianyin Mountain.

21:33.750 --> 21:35.280
My cultivation is shallow.

21:35.680 --> 21:36.790
I have not yet had the fortune

21:36.790 --> 21:38.250
to pass through that gate.

21:46.680 --> 21:48.740
Are you willing to cultivate with me?

21:51.440 --> 21:52.100
No, thanks.

21:52.920 --> 21:54.920
Since childhood, I've been determined to
join Tianyin Mountain

21:54.920 --> 21:57.050
and cultivate the Path of Detachment.

21:57.590 --> 21:58.200
Why?

21:58.830 --> 22:00.090
To attain the Great Way

22:00.270 --> 22:02.000
and protect all living beings.

22:04.270 --> 22:05.880
If you cultivate the Path of Detachment,

22:05.880 --> 22:08.010
how can you protect all living beings?

22:08.640 --> 22:09.550
Govern by law,

22:10.310 --> 22:12.070
and judge all by the same measure.

22:12.070 --> 22:13.600
The law spares no nobility,

22:13.730 --> 22:15.730
just as a mirror does not hide flaws.

22:15.920 --> 22:16.720
Whose law?

22:17.480 --> 22:19.680
The righteous laws of the Heavenly Way.

22:25.340 --> 22:26.670
Heaven knows no emotion

22:26.880 --> 22:29.000
and sees all things as but specks of dust.

22:29.000 --> 22:30.480
Since you follow the Heavenly Way,

22:30.480 --> 22:32.340
you should conform to its nature:

22:32.790 --> 22:35.650
the strong prey upon the weak,
the fittest survive,

22:35.720 --> 22:38.450
and all things live and perish
in endless cycles.

22:38.680 --> 22:40.880
What need is there for you to intervene?

22:42.750 --> 22:44.030
Under the Heavenly Way,

22:44.030 --> 22:45.440
the Way of Humanity has collapsed,

22:45.440 --> 22:47.170
and injustice runs unchecked.

22:47.350 --> 22:48.960
The powerful act without restraint,

22:48.960 --> 22:50.160
fabricating justifications

22:50.160 --> 22:51.290
to do as they please.

22:51.830 --> 22:53.750
They treat human lives like weeds,

22:53.750 --> 22:55.680
seizing profits for their own use,

22:55.680 --> 22:57.210
making the strong stronger

22:57.270 --> 22:58.670
and the weak even weaker.

22:59.110 --> 23:01.040
The strong are infinitely greedy,

23:01.070 --> 23:02.270
plundering by force,

23:02.510 --> 23:04.440
while the weak struggle humbly to survive,

23:04.440 --> 23:05.840
suffering unspeakably.

23:06.480 --> 23:07.140
Therefore,

23:07.350 --> 23:08.480
since I've chosen

23:08.480 --> 23:09.680
to practice this path

23:09.830 --> 23:11.160
and gained my power

23:11.590 --> 23:13.440
through the teachings of the Heavenly Way,

23:13.440 --> 23:14.900
I have the responsibility

23:15.110 --> 23:16.160
to act upon it

23:16.680 --> 23:17.720
and right what is wrong.

23:17.720 --> 23:18.400
Naive!

23:20.980 --> 23:21.840
Do you know that

23:22.030 --> 23:23.680
although most of us cultivators

23:23.680 --> 23:25.710
claim to follow the Heavenly Way,

23:26.110 --> 23:26.880
in reality,

23:27.400 --> 23:29.020
they practice the Way of Humanity?

23:29.020 --> 23:30.550
What is the Way of Humanity?

23:30.680 --> 23:32.150
The Way is a road.

23:32.750 --> 23:34.140
When enough people walk it,

23:34.140 --> 23:35.430
it becomes

23:35.450 --> 23:36.510
the established order.

23:36.510 --> 23:38.840
To go against it
and forge a different road

23:38.960 --> 23:41.420
will only bring harm
to yourself and others.

23:44.680 --> 23:46.280
Thank you for your guidance,

23:46.350 --> 23:47.350
but I do not agree.

23:52.480 --> 23:54.110
Your heart is not free of attachment.

23:54.110 --> 23:56.270
The mortal world still
has its hold on you.

23:56.270 --> 23:57.330
Little do you know,

23:57.750 --> 23:59.920
benevolence is a blade that cuts slowly,

23:59.920 --> 24:02.250
and love is a poison
that gnaws to the bone.

24:02.310 --> 24:03.550
To seek gain and avoid harm,

24:03.550 --> 24:04.510
and to act on one's desires—

24:04.510 --> 24:05.640
that is human nature.

24:05.640 --> 24:06.440
And yet you...

24:07.440 --> 24:09.550
care about even just a few lives enough

24:09.550 --> 24:10.660
for them to weigh on

24:10.960 --> 24:11.960
your conscience.

24:12.720 --> 24:14.240
How, then, will you ever grasp

24:14.240 --> 24:16.370
the essence of the Path of Detachment?

24:17.070 --> 24:19.270
If you can't see through this delusion,

24:19.480 --> 24:21.310
it will one day devour you.

24:27.270 --> 24:28.800
I thought too highly of you.

24:29.400 --> 24:30.660
Where are you heading?

24:30.920 --> 24:31.650
North Xiang.

24:34.590 --> 24:35.920
We happen to be going the same way.

24:35.920 --> 24:37.780
I still have matters to attend to.

24:37.880 --> 24:40.010
I can only leave once they are settled.

24:40.310 --> 24:42.240
The path I take is different from yours,

24:42.240 --> 24:43.970
so we're not going the same way.

24:52.240 --> 24:53.240
I'll be going now.

25:13.790 --> 25:14.440
Guys,

25:15.200 --> 25:16.400
look who it is.

25:17.070 --> 25:19.000
We've met that little buddy again.

25:28.240 --> 25:29.880
Murder! Murder!

25:37.960 --> 25:39.110
One missing.

25:46.830 --> 25:48.630
Please... Please don't kill me!

25:48.750 --> 25:49.950
Please don't kill me!

25:50.030 --> 25:51.230
Please don't kill me!

26:06.110 --> 26:07.310
M-Murder!

26:08.640 --> 26:09.400
Murder!

26:12.880 --> 26:13.750
Murder!

26:24.380 --> 26:26.440
[Xutuo City]

26:25.030 --> 26:27.120
One tael of silver per draw!

26:27.160 --> 26:27.750
Come on!

26:27.750 --> 26:29.920
Pay first, then draw a ticket!

26:30.400 --> 26:31.310
One tael of silver—

26:31.310 --> 26:33.350
no tricks, no scams,

26:33.440 --> 26:34.400
and it just might

26:34.420 --> 26:36.480
tell your fortune for the whole year!

26:36.510 --> 26:39.000
If you draw this slip for the grand prize,

26:39.830 --> 26:42.510
this horse will be yours for free!

26:43.160 --> 26:43.830
Come on!

26:43.830 --> 26:45.290
Really? I'll give it a try!

26:46.200 --> 26:46.960
One draw!

26:46.960 --> 26:48.270
One draw—one tael!

26:48.310 --> 26:49.160
Come and draw!

26:49.350 --> 26:49.950
Slow down.

26:50.510 --> 26:51.590
-How is it?
-Don't rush!

26:51.590 --> 26:51.960
Don't rush.

26:51.960 --> 26:52.550
Did you win?

26:52.550 --> 26:53.000
No.

26:53.400 --> 26:54.640
Check quickly if you won.

26:54.640 --> 26:55.480
There are draws for everyone.

26:55.480 --> 26:56.400
Did anyone win?

26:56.720 --> 26:57.310
Did you win?

26:57.310 --> 26:58.270
Did anyone win?

26:58.590 --> 26:59.510
No, no.

26:59.510 --> 27:00.830
It's fine if you didn't win!

27:00.830 --> 27:01.590
Give me another draw!

27:01.590 --> 27:02.700
Buddy, no luck this time just means

27:02.700 --> 27:04.560
the grand prize is still in there,

27:04.880 --> 27:07.160
waiting for the really lucky one!

27:07.750 --> 27:09.000
This is a horse!

27:09.270 --> 27:10.830
It's a living horse!

27:11.070 --> 27:11.960
A horse—

27:12.360 --> 27:14.080
how much hard work

27:14.110 --> 27:16.170
does it take to earn yourself a horse?

27:16.680 --> 27:17.830
Isn't this a scam?

27:17.830 --> 27:19.000
I've drawn several times

27:19.000 --> 27:20.060
and never won once.

27:20.160 --> 27:21.440
Listen to yourself!

27:21.510 --> 27:22.110
This is definitely a scam!

27:22.110 --> 27:23.240
Everyone here saw me

27:23.270 --> 27:25.240
put the grand prize ticket in
with their own eyes.

27:25.240 --> 27:26.270
You didn't draw it;

27:26.270 --> 27:28.600
that just means your luck hasn't come yet!

27:28.640 --> 27:30.570
There are only so many blank slips!

27:30.830 --> 27:32.200
The more blanks that get drawn,

27:32.200 --> 27:33.110
the better

27:33.480 --> 27:35.030
your chances!

27:35.610 --> 27:36.400
Are you in or not?

27:36.400 --> 27:37.070
In or not?

27:37.070 --> 27:38.510
Come on, I'll draw five more!

27:38.510 --> 27:39.400
Come on!

27:39.720 --> 27:40.790
Come on!

27:40.790 --> 27:42.790
One tael per draw!

27:45.120 --> 27:46.380
Okay! Come on!

27:46.960 --> 27:48.160
Okay, draw your slip!

27:48.160 --> 27:49.110
Big win, big win!

27:49.160 --> 27:50.480
Your chance to get rich is here!

27:50.480 --> 27:51.110
Let's see

27:51.310 --> 27:53.310
how this buddy's luck is.

27:53.790 --> 27:54.680
I'll draw...

27:54.880 --> 27:55.510
Okay.

27:56.310 --> 27:57.610
Let's see if you won.

27:57.640 --> 27:58.170
How is it?

27:58.200 --> 27:59.960
Let's see. Let's see!

27:58.240 --> 27:59.750
[Horse]

28:00.270 --> 28:01.270
It has the character "horse" on it.

28:01.270 --> 28:02.270
What does it mean?

28:02.510 --> 28:03.440
You won! You won!

28:03.440 --> 28:04.500
Congratulations!

28:04.510 --> 28:05.550
You won! You won!

28:06.200 --> 28:07.260
This little buddy,

28:07.440 --> 28:09.790
one look at you and I can tell
you're a man of great fortune!

28:09.790 --> 28:11.190
Would you like the horse,

28:11.240 --> 28:13.100
or would you prefer to cash it out?

28:13.160 --> 28:14.290
I can cash it out too?

28:14.350 --> 28:15.200
Of course!

28:15.510 --> 28:17.240
Whatever the market price of the horse is,

28:17.240 --> 28:19.170
I'll give you the amount in silver!

28:19.350 --> 28:20.240
Then I want silver!

28:20.240 --> 28:21.550
Okay! Okay!

28:23.070 --> 28:24.330
You've struck it rich!

28:24.640 --> 28:25.920
Congratulations, buddy.

28:25.920 --> 28:27.480
You're a man of great wealth and fortune!

28:27.480 --> 28:30.210
-Thank you.
-Congratulations on your windfall!

28:30.400 --> 28:31.350
This is the money.

28:31.350 --> 28:32.270
We're even now!

28:32.350 --> 28:32.790
Okay.

28:33.440 --> 28:34.000
Okay.

28:35.720 --> 28:36.480
Come on.

28:38.000 --> 28:39.730
I'm returning the horse to you.

28:40.720 --> 28:42.920
And here is the money we promised you.

28:43.270 --> 28:44.130
We're settled.

28:44.640 --> 28:45.840
Thank you. Thank you.

28:47.640 --> 28:48.240
Take care!

28:48.240 --> 28:49.310
The water pouch is filled.

28:49.310 --> 28:50.000
In the bag,

28:50.020 --> 28:51.070
there are 20 flatbreads.

28:51.070 --> 28:52.130
Enough for 10 days.

28:52.720 --> 28:53.320
Thank you.

28:59.640 --> 29:00.480
What is this?

29:01.030 --> 29:02.000
I forgot to tell you.

29:02.000 --> 29:03.400
These are tamarind candies
from our shop,

29:03.400 --> 29:04.260
our specialty.

29:04.400 --> 29:05.680
Have a piece when you're feeling drowsy—

29:05.680 --> 29:07.200
it can sharpen the mind
and clear the head.

29:07.200 --> 29:07.800
Thank you.

29:07.880 --> 29:09.110
Senior, try one.

29:15.400 --> 29:16.130
It's so sour.

29:16.550 --> 29:18.640
Spit it out.
Be careful not to ruin your teeth.

29:18.640 --> 29:20.310
How can it refresh your mind
if it's not sour?

29:20.310 --> 29:21.110
You two enjoy.

29:21.160 --> 29:22.030
I'll get back to work.

29:22.030 --> 29:23.630
Call me if you need anything.

29:33.590 --> 29:34.340
Let's go.

29:36.440 --> 29:38.040
You can give it a try. Come on.

29:39.880 --> 29:40.880
Come on, let's go.

29:44.030 --> 29:45.200
Done shopping. Let's head home.

29:45.200 --> 29:47.260
Freshly baked meat buns, piping hot!

29:55.550 --> 29:56.960
You said earlier there was only one road

29:56.960 --> 29:58.310
into the heart of North Xiang,

29:58.310 --> 29:59.920
and that's why we traveled together.

29:59.920 --> 30:01.830
Now we're in the city,
and there are roads everywhere.

30:01.830 --> 30:03.070
Why are you still following us?

30:03.070 --> 30:03.590
What?

30:04.230 --> 30:05.490
You really want to die?

30:05.510 --> 30:06.350
No, no.

30:07.080 --> 30:07.890
We owe you both

30:07.920 --> 30:09.960
a great deal for looking after us
along the way.

30:09.960 --> 30:11.020
We made some money,

30:11.440 --> 30:13.000
so we'd like to treat you to a meal.

30:13.000 --> 30:13.830
You scammed the money.

30:13.830 --> 30:14.960
We want no part of it.

30:15.190 --> 30:16.720
How is that a scam?

30:17.000 --> 30:18.350
It was all voluntary.

30:18.590 --> 30:19.400
Make way, make way!

30:19.400 --> 30:21.000
-Out of the way!
-Move aside!

30:21.270 --> 30:22.510
It's those scammers.

30:22.790 --> 30:24.530
They cheated me out of a lot of money!

30:24.530 --> 30:26.200
You chose to play—
and now you can't accept the loss?

30:26.200 --> 30:27.440
What are you standing there for? Run!

30:27.440 --> 30:27.880
After them!

30:27.880 --> 30:28.410
Get them!

30:28.640 --> 30:30.240
They're the ones who cheated me!

30:30.240 --> 30:30.900
After them!

30:34.270 --> 30:34.880
Senior.

30:35.880 --> 30:37.000
No need to stir up trouble.

30:37.000 --> 30:37.530
Let's go.

30:38.830 --> 30:40.960
Bishui Branch has started
seizing people again!

30:40.960 --> 30:41.720
They took the leader

30:41.720 --> 30:42.920
of the Fengyuan Camel Caravan earlier

30:42.920 --> 30:44.000
and still haven't released him.

30:44.000 --> 30:45.480
I can't get my goods transported out.

30:45.480 --> 30:47.080
Who knows when this will end?

30:47.200 --> 30:48.960
Don't wait for him. He's not coming out.

30:48.960 --> 30:49.840
How would you know?

30:49.840 --> 30:51.070
Last time he was helping me move cargo

30:51.070 --> 30:52.160
when someone from the Bishui Branch came

30:52.160 --> 30:53.880
and said something about "water."

30:53.880 --> 30:55.020
Then he acted like he was possessed,

30:55.020 --> 30:56.280
abandoned his camel caravan, and ran away.

30:56.280 --> 30:57.310
He only came back recently,

30:57.310 --> 30:58.680
saying he'd been to the Central Plains

30:58.680 --> 31:00.000
and brought back a slaughterer

31:00.000 --> 31:00.960
who wiped out

31:00.960 --> 31:02.420
the entire Bishui Branch.

31:03.240 --> 31:03.790
Really?

31:07.240 --> 31:08.440
Please wait, you two.

31:08.830 --> 31:09.510
Miss,

31:09.640 --> 31:10.640
do you need something?

31:10.640 --> 31:11.440
I'd like to ask

31:11.480 --> 31:12.480
about the caravan leader

31:12.480 --> 31:13.610
you just mentioned.

31:13.640 --> 31:14.900
What does he look like?

31:24.270 --> 31:25.040
I'll go.

31:25.240 --> 31:26.240
You wait for me here.

31:26.240 --> 31:27.300
Let's go together.

31:34.630 --> 31:35.520
Another day,

31:35.550 --> 31:36.950
and still nothing for us.

31:37.160 --> 31:38.360
Come on, let's drink!

31:38.510 --> 31:39.030
Cheers!

32:30.590 --> 32:31.250
It's you...

32:32.790 --> 32:33.880
You saved me.

32:35.070 --> 32:37.110
I have something I want to ask you.

32:38.200 --> 32:38.880
Okay.

32:41.880 --> 32:42.480
And then,

32:42.830 --> 32:44.030
he let me go.

32:44.680 --> 32:45.550
But I heard

32:46.350 --> 32:47.790
that later that night, someone

32:47.790 --> 32:49.920
killed everyone at the Bishui Branch.

32:50.480 --> 32:51.440
That's a branch

32:51.440 --> 32:52.640
of the Qinghong Sect.

32:52.830 --> 32:54.240
They usually had over 100 people

32:54.240 --> 32:55.070
stationed there,

32:55.070 --> 32:56.880
all highly skilled in martial arts.

32:56.880 --> 32:58.590
Legend has it that the Branch Master

32:58.590 --> 33:00.510
had reached the Golden Core Stage.

33:00.510 --> 33:01.070
However,

33:01.750 --> 33:02.790
they all died.

33:03.790 --> 33:05.050
Every last one of them.

33:08.750 --> 33:09.440
That person

33:09.510 --> 33:11.170
should be your friend, right?

33:11.400 --> 33:12.400
He traveled thousands of miles

33:12.400 --> 33:13.310
to avenge you.

33:13.960 --> 33:15.830
He must value you very much.

33:20.160 --> 33:20.720
Senior,

33:21.270 --> 33:22.070
are you okay?

33:23.550 --> 33:24.310
I'm fine.

33:41.190 --> 33:46.020
♪ Spending a lifetime,
I ask myself what I first sought ♪

33:47.200 --> 33:51.960
♪ What is it my heart truly desires? ♪

33:52.460 --> 33:55.450
♪ Step by step up the immortal stairway ♪

33:55.720 --> 33:57.750
I was under a Spell of Utterance before—

33:55.870 --> 33:58.620
♪ Paved with countless lost souls ♪

33:58.480 --> 33:59.310
every time I drank water, I'd vomit.

33:58.900 --> 34:04.850
♪ Who would dare destroy the ladder
to immortality and end the path? ♪

33:59.920 --> 34:02.240
But that day, it suddenly lifted.

34:02.720 --> 34:03.720
Suddenly lifted?

34:04.200 --> 34:05.880
Then there's no need to take your pulse.

34:05.190 --> 34:10.150
♪ The sun blazes over the earth ♪

34:06.350 --> 34:08.230
So you know how the spell was lifted,
Divine Doctor Su?

34:08.230 --> 34:09.360
How else?

34:09.630 --> 34:11.159
It must have been pure luck.

34:11.170 --> 34:16.199
♪ Yet it cannot warm
every cold home below ♪

34:11.630 --> 34:12.760
Don't overthink it.

34:13.190 --> 34:14.630
When Lu Qianqiao comes back,

34:14.630 --> 34:15.670
he will tell you

34:15.840 --> 34:17.190
what really happened.

34:16.219 --> 34:19.820
♪ I've heard cries that rend the heavens ♪

34:18.280 --> 34:20.360
The Spell of Utterance can only be cast
by someone of a higher cultivation rank

34:19.969 --> 34:22.790
♪ I hear the shame of parting ♪

34:20.360 --> 34:21.960
upon someone of a lower rank.

34:22.480 --> 34:23.360
You're not very high-ranked.

34:22.810 --> 34:25.380
♪ This immortal path admired by all ♪

34:23.710 --> 34:25.400
It's normal you didn't sense it.

34:25.400 --> 34:28.280
♪ Can exist, or not exist ♪

34:26.190 --> 34:28.030
Since you consider me your senior,

34:28.030 --> 34:29.110
I won't let you die.

34:28.310 --> 34:30.960
♪ Once again I see
the world's cold indifference ♪

34:29.960 --> 34:31.590
I have matters to attend to
and must leave the valley for a while.

34:30.989 --> 34:34.230
♪ Bending what I've cherished
all my life ♪

34:32.150 --> 34:33.630
I won't be able to look after you.

34:33.630 --> 34:34.510
After I leave,

34:34.260 --> 34:39.610
♪ Illusions and vanity blind the eyes,
how could one still care ♪

34:34.710 --> 34:36.440
you must keep practicing
the Fish Drinking Technique.

34:36.440 --> 34:37.370
Don't slack off.

34:38.230 --> 34:38.960
I will.

34:40.570 --> 34:43.350
♪ To let all walk ♪

34:41.030 --> 34:41.670
Mr. Lu.

34:43.380 --> 34:46.310
♪ The road to immortality ♪

34:45.150 --> 34:46.330
Is what you're going to do

34:46.330 --> 34:52.560
♪ I fear not defying
immortal laws and sacred precepts ♪

34:46.670 --> 34:47.440
dangerous?

34:48.840 --> 34:49.699
Not dangerous.

34:52.790 --> 34:56.409
♪ Let sin be punished,
let desire be destroyed ♪

34:57.350 --> 35:04.300
♪ Yet the heart must never be forsaken ♪

35:02.280 --> 35:03.280
I have to find him.

35:07.030 --> 35:07.960
I need to see him.

35:20.220 --> 35:20.820
Master Lu,

35:21.230 --> 35:22.710
how is Changyuan's injury?

35:22.710 --> 35:24.040
The wound has festered,

35:24.110 --> 35:25.590
and the poison has spread to
the vital organs.

35:25.590 --> 35:27.030
If the Lord of Rust-Sword and Lu Zhanying

35:27.030 --> 35:28.000
do not return
with the Dragon Subduing Grass

35:28.000 --> 35:29.030
before sunset,

35:29.800 --> 35:30.400
I'm afraid

35:31.000 --> 35:32.590
he won't make it through the night.

35:32.590 --> 35:34.030
A black sandstorm has risen outside.

35:34.030 --> 35:35.490
God knows when it'll pass.

35:35.690 --> 35:37.400
I'm worried that
even if they find the herb,

35:37.400 --> 35:39.000
they won't be able to find their way back.

35:39.000 --> 35:39.550
No.

35:40.030 --> 35:41.030
I'll go find them.

35:41.670 --> 35:43.230
Don't make things worse!

35:43.550 --> 35:44.550
The storm is too strong!

35:44.550 --> 35:45.800
No one can move through it!

35:45.800 --> 35:47.070
Where are you going to find them?

35:47.070 --> 35:48.270
Then what do we do now?

35:49.000 --> 35:49.590
Found it!

35:49.880 --> 35:50.510
Found it!

35:52.630 --> 35:54.630
We found the Dragon Subduing Grass.

35:55.510 --> 35:56.710
See if this is enough.

35:58.550 --> 36:00.760
Take five qian
and boil it into a decoction.

36:00.760 --> 36:02.000
Boil three bowls down to one.

36:02.000 --> 36:03.080
Then take some more, mash it,

36:03.080 --> 36:03.920
and apply it to the wound.

36:03.920 --> 36:04.720
Okay, I'll go.

36:05.400 --> 36:06.800
I-I'll go with him.

36:10.880 --> 36:14.400
[Caiyuan Inn]

36:24.230 --> 36:25.430
Please have some tea.

36:31.320 --> 36:32.400
Immortal,

36:32.880 --> 36:34.480
do you need me for something?

36:35.760 --> 36:36.820
I once heard you say

36:37.210 --> 36:39.360
that you joined Dongting Mountain
when you were young

36:39.360 --> 36:41.360
and studied under the Crazy Taoist.

36:41.630 --> 36:42.570
Is that true?

36:42.760 --> 36:43.800
Absolutely true.

36:44.510 --> 36:45.360
It's just

36:45.920 --> 36:47.380
that you don't believe it.

36:48.670 --> 36:49.870
Among the War Demons,

36:49.880 --> 36:51.920
there is a technique called Descent,

36:51.920 --> 36:54.030
which allows one
to control another from afar.

36:54.030 --> 36:54.890
As far as I know,

36:55.630 --> 36:56.710
the Crazy Taoist also has

36:56.710 --> 36:57.840
a similar secret art

36:58.190 --> 36:59.720
called Spirit Projection.

37:00.590 --> 37:01.950
As long as you've seen a person,

37:01.950 --> 37:03.420
you can use this secret art

37:03.630 --> 37:04.880
to project your spirit and will

37:04.880 --> 37:06.030
onto them

37:06.110 --> 37:07.040
and talk to them.

37:08.110 --> 37:09.510
Then,

37:10.590 --> 37:11.440
do you know how to do that?

37:11.440 --> 37:11.920
Yes.

37:13.000 --> 37:15.550
I use it on Craftsman Zhu and Shi Wen

37:15.880 --> 37:17.190
all the time.

37:17.570 --> 37:18.830
It's very convenient.

37:19.360 --> 37:21.070
But it only works on

37:21.590 --> 37:24.030
Zhu Dajian and Shi Wen when I use it.

37:24.230 --> 37:26.290
It doesn't work on anyone else at all.

37:27.230 --> 37:27.840
Why?

37:28.280 --> 37:30.800
The first principle
of Spirit Projection is that,

37:30.800 --> 37:32.000
to use it,

37:32.430 --> 37:34.490
one must find the gate to
the other person's divine sense

37:34.490 --> 37:37.150
within one's own spiritual sea
of divine sense.

37:37.760 --> 37:38.490
Understand?

37:39.030 --> 37:39.510
No.

37:39.860 --> 37:40.700
Simply put,

37:41.360 --> 37:41.960
you have to

37:42.070 --> 37:44.300
find the other person's

37:44.680 --> 37:46.200
Gate of Divine Sense

37:46.220 --> 37:47.630
within your own spiritual sea.

37:47.630 --> 37:48.190
And

37:48.550 --> 37:50.880
your divine sense
must pass through that gate

37:50.880 --> 37:52.510
and enter the other person's spiritual sea

37:52.510 --> 37:55.280
before you can establish
a connection with them.

37:56.360 --> 37:58.220
Everyone we've ever encountered

37:58.360 --> 37:59.320
leaves an imprint

37:59.320 --> 38:00.720
upon our spiritual seas.

38:01.070 --> 38:03.450
That's the so-called gate.

38:03.840 --> 38:04.960
If you can identify

38:04.960 --> 38:06.490
which gate belongs to whom,

38:06.800 --> 38:08.730
you can perform Spirit Projection

38:08.800 --> 38:09.920
and easily

38:10.440 --> 38:12.230
find the person you're looking for.

38:12.230 --> 38:12.920
But

38:13.210 --> 38:15.010
the people we've met in our lives

38:15.400 --> 38:16.590
are far too many.

38:17.590 --> 38:18.770
Strangers count too?

38:18.770 --> 38:19.630
They all count.

38:20.030 --> 38:22.090
People you know and people you don't,

38:22.280 --> 38:24.230
including street vendors,

38:24.510 --> 38:25.910
pedestrians on the road,

38:25.920 --> 38:27.120
and guests next door—

38:27.440 --> 38:28.960
anyone you have ever laid eyes on

38:28.960 --> 38:31.030
leaves a gate in your spiritual sea.

38:32.400 --> 38:33.260
Think about it—

38:34.090 --> 38:35.350
how many would that be?

38:36.070 --> 38:37.990
Would you try them one by one?

38:38.280 --> 38:39.550
It'd drain too much of your energy.

38:39.550 --> 38:41.110
You simply couldn't endure it.

38:41.110 --> 38:41.840
But

38:42.070 --> 38:43.150
you've used it

38:43.280 --> 38:45.030
to contact Zhu Dajian and Shi Wen before.

38:45.030 --> 38:46.510
That's because I know them

38:46.710 --> 38:47.590
very well.

38:48.030 --> 38:48.630
And

38:49.190 --> 38:50.710
I have the tokens

38:50.960 --> 38:51.950
they usually use.

38:51.950 --> 38:52.480
Besides,

38:52.710 --> 38:54.880
they're usually not far from me,

38:55.140 --> 38:56.300
so it's easy.

38:56.750 --> 38:57.920
But your case is different.

38:57.920 --> 38:59.120
Do you know the person

38:59.760 --> 39:01.160
you are looking for well?

39:01.400 --> 39:02.920
Do you know where he is?

39:03.670 --> 39:04.870
I don't know him well.

39:05.590 --> 39:06.590
Not at all.

39:07.440 --> 39:09.440
And I have no idea where he is either.

39:09.510 --> 39:10.570
But I must find him.

39:11.510 --> 39:12.970
He's very important to me.

39:15.230 --> 39:16.110
Can you help me?

39:36.030 --> 39:38.440
Since you have no token

39:39.630 --> 39:40.920
and don't know

39:41.280 --> 39:42.960
the person's location,

39:43.440 --> 39:44.570
we can only initiate

39:45.030 --> 39:46.360
the Heaven-Offering Ritual.

39:46.360 --> 39:47.110
The Heaven-Offering Ritual?

39:47.110 --> 39:47.760
Yes.

39:48.960 --> 39:51.150
Five jars of wine to honor the ancestors
and offer to the gods.

39:51.150 --> 39:53.280
Five cups of tea to clear the mind
and sharpen sight.

39:53.280 --> 39:55.340
Burn incense to offer to the heavens.

39:55.800 --> 39:57.860
Borrow the power of the Five Elements

39:58.030 --> 40:00.830
to project your spirit
across thousands of miles.

40:02.360 --> 40:03.880
Immortal, are you ready?

40:05.320 --> 40:06.030
I'm ready.

40:20.480 --> 40:23.140
I, Tai Shiqian,
disciple of Dongting Mountain,

40:23.150 --> 40:26.280
hereby solemnly declare to Heaven!
I draw upon Heaven's power,

40:26.280 --> 40:30.940
using the Five Elements as a medium to
project the spirit across thousands of miles!

40:44.590 --> 40:47.840
The ebb and flow of Yin and Yang
are wondrous and infinite.

40:48.110 --> 40:50.440
The solstices return to the Nine Palaces.

40:50.710 --> 40:53.070
Should you fully grasp the principles
of Yin and Yang,

40:53.070 --> 40:55.880
heaven and earth shall be held
in the palm of your hand!

40:55.880 --> 40:56.510
Open!

41:09.150 --> 41:11.210
Three to the left, seven to the right.

41:12.230 --> 41:14.290
Nine crowns above, one treads below.

41:14.760 --> 41:16.490
Two and four are the shoulders,

41:16.880 --> 41:18.540
and six and eight are the feet.

41:19.710 --> 41:21.110
Five rests at the center,

41:21.800 --> 41:23.860
filling the core and making it whole.

41:33.950 --> 41:36.070
[Xin Mei's Spiritual Sea]

41:41.800 --> 41:43.400
Immortal, please remember:

41:43.920 --> 41:46.030
you must remain calm and focused

41:46.320 --> 41:48.320
and safeguard your primordial spirit.

41:48.320 --> 41:50.180
If you truly cannot find the gate,

41:50.400 --> 41:52.800
do not force it.
